init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You continue your work, but the bee continues to speak.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the bee, and she looks back at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is a beautiful bee, with a purple and black striped body, and a yellow and black striped head.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to play along with the bee, just to see where it goes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, Felicity, I'm glad you've finally found me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What do you want from me?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I want to serve you, your majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, Felicity, but I'm not a bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Felicity is not pleased with your answer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, Felicity, but I can't help you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You say, and you walk away from the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee follows you, and begins to yell at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You can't do this, you're our queen!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You begin to run away from them, but they are too many.
